'''Arhiva Națională de Filme''' is a [[film archive]] located in [[Bucharest]], [[Romania]]. It is a member of the [[Association of European Film Archives and Cinematheques]].<ref>[http://www.ace-film.eu/?page_id=475/ ACE members list]</ref>
== References == {{reflist}}
== External links == * http://www.anf-cinemateca.ro
[[Category:Film archives]] [[Category:Government agencies established in 1957]] [[Category:1957 establishments in Romania]] [[Category:Independent government agencies of Romania]] [[Category:Archives in Romania]]
{{Film-org-stub}}

