{{DISPLAYTITLE:''Helios'' (encyclopedia)}}
{{unreferenced|date=October 2015}}
[[File:Helios-encyclopaedia.jpg|thumb|The books, note that one is divided in two parts]]
'''''Helios''''', more fully the '''''Helios New Encyclopedic Dictionary''''' ({{lang-el|Νεώτερο Εγκυκλοπαιδικό Λεξικό Ηλίου}} or: Νεώτερον Εγκυκλοπαιδικόν Λεξικόν Ήλιος), is a [[general knowledge]] Greek [[encyclopaedia]]. Its publication commenced in 1945 while its second edition was completed in 1960, comprising 18 volumes.

